name: My Resting Place
description: My favorite place in Dayuan, Taiwan. I was able to stay at that building you see here in the photo during my quarantine time after arriving in Taiwan in 2020. I got some much needed rest. The entire area is still being developed so there isn't much around, but I like it that way. Now that I'm living in the city and there are constant noises all around me, I really miss the quiet.
